Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 08:38:54 +1000
Subject: [PATCH] Support additional dense runtime-slice families

---
 src/models/cohere2.cpp    | 20 ++++++++++++++++----
 src/models/command-r.cpp  | 20 ++++++++++++++++----
